init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She looked at him, then at the popcorn bowl, then back at him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She had dated this man four times before?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She closed it behind him and leaned against it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She had a lot to think about.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She went to bed that night and slept fitfully.
